00:35:53,940 --> 00:35:56,610
Kulihat kau menggeledah di sana.

451
00:35:56,610 --> 00:35:58,390
Apa yang kau cari?

452
00:35:59,730 --> 00:36:01,460
Aku tidak menggeledah apapun...

453
00:36:02,160 --> 00:36:04,570
Beberapa koinku jatuh,
