618
00:46:08,290 --> 00:46:11,460
Jadi kau juga malas-malasan
seperti Si Tn Warm itu.

619
00:46:11,460 --> 00:46:16,200
Dia mengemudikan mobil merah
sangat cepat di jalanan kota ini...

620
00:46:16,200 --> 00:46:18,330
Hae Sil hampir tertabrak!

621
00:46:18,330 --> 00:46:20,240
- Sungguh?
- Dia melakukannya!

622
00:46:21,990 --> 00:46:23,730
Mereka bilang apa?

623
00:46:23,730 --> 00:46:25,860
